STATE EX REL. THIGPEN
v.
SUTULA 2019-0670 Supreme Court of Ohio. July 16, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENT

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSAL

Appellant has not filed a merit brief, due July 10, 2019, in compliance with the Rules of Practice of the Supreme Court of Ohio and therefore has failed to prosecute this cause with the requisite diligence. Cause dismissed.
